{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_51_01",
  "title": "神崎莉央 1話 莉央のわがまま",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――雑誌企画『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Magazine project: Miracle☆Idol Birthday!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "インタビュー中",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――During the interview",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.0533332269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、ありがたいことに\n誕生日当日はお仕事が入っています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ thankfully…\n…I have work on my birthday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.2999996263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.4533335129
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "プレゼントにほしいもの……？\nそうですね……しいて挙げるとすれば――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something I want as a present…?\nWell… if I had to pick something――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.1999998171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――インタビュー後のレッスンスタジオ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Lesson studio after the interview",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.0333337227,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1866.6653075999982,
          "startTime": 18.8999990303
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-noon",
      "startTime": 18.4666664838
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。お疲れ、莉央\n意外と終わるの早かったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ good work Rio.\nYou finished surprisingly early.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.7333329359,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "葵こそ、随分と余裕そうじゃない\n今日の練習はもう終わったのかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem pretty relaxed yourself‚ Aoi.\nAre you already done with practice today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.715895756,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "とっくに終わったよ。今は休憩中なんだ\nこれを読んでたところ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I finished a while ago. I'm on break now.\nI was reading this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.0333334445,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4447.483150199996,
          "startTime": 35.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "あら、過去の\n『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』の記事ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ an article…\n…from Miracle☆Idol Birthday!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.4839657861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "『アイドルの願いごとを叶える誕生日企画』だって\n芽衣も渚も好き放題やらせてもらったみたいだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a \"Birthday Project to Grant Idols' Wishes\".\nMei and Nagisa seem to have gotten whatever they wanted.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.8666624545,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "莉央、さっきそれのインタビューを受けてたんだよね\n何をお願いしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio‚ you were interviewed for that earlier‚ right?\nWhat did you wish for?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.3333291212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに特別なことは言ってないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't say anything particularly special.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.0240993897,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、パンケーキの布団で寝たいとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ like you want to sleep in a pancake blanket‚ or something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.6473193407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "違うわよ\nもっと現実的な……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No.\nSomething more realistic…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.3597696541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "パンケーキの布団だって、やろうと思えば出来るよ\nまず莉央サイズの大きな生地を用意して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can even make a pancake blanket if you really want to.\nFirst‚ you prepare a large dough the size of Rio…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.4999881585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "やらないわよ！　そういうことじゃないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won't! That's not what I meant!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.5125942231,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、パンケーキで作った服を着て\n海外のファッションショーに出たいとか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ you want to wear clothes made of pancakes…\n…and appear in a fashion show overseas?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.2333204746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "パンケーキになる発想から離れなさい\n私がお願いしたのは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Get rid of the idea of becoming a pancake.\nWhat I wished for…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.0194877543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "『今まで食べたことのないパンケーキ』よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…is \"A pancake I've never had before\".",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.354226764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱりパンケーキじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's still pancakes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.4636803627,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "……纏うのと食べるのは別でしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Wearing it and eating it are different things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.7103439014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "私が知らない穴場のお店があったら\n教えてもらおうと思ったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought I'd ask them to tell me\nabout decent pancake places that I never tried.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.3478362448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、スタッフさんがちょっと戸惑っていて\nやっぱり違うものが良かったかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But the staff seemed a little confused.\nso maybe I should have wished for something else.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.1142212467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "莉央がスタッフを困らせるなんてめずらしいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's rare for Rio to trouble the staff.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.8137222608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "困らせたつもりはないわ！　今思いつくほしいものが\n知らないお店の情報ってだけで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't mean to trouble them! It's just that the only thing I want right now\nis information about an unknown shop…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.6289603151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "……ふーん。今ほしいもの、か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hmm. Something you want right now‚ huh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.49573013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "な、何よ\n案外普通だったでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-What?\nWasn't it surprisingly normal?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.9875665263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり莉央は真面目だね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio‚ you're really serious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.0403784754,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3459.6215245999956,
          "startTime": 128.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと。どこ行くのよ\n本当に今日の練習は終わり？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ where are you going?\nAre you really done with practice today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.613795447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "飲み物を買ってくるだけだよ。すぐ戻る",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm just going to buy drinks. I'll be right back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.8971390091,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4851.413916900015,
          "startTime": 138.748552926
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.2404785319
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
