      "text": "『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』の企画で\n莉央がわがままを言ったみたいなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like Rio made a selfish request\nfor the Miracle☆Idol Birthday! project.",
        "id": ""
