      "text": "『今まで食べたことのないパンケーキ』って注文さ\n本当に莉央はパンケーキが好きだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She requested \"A pancake I've never had before\".\nRio really loves pancakes‚ doesn't she?",
        "id": ""
